<h1>AsiaInspection Acquires CHB Laboratory to Strengthen Consumer Goods Testing and Certification Capabilities</h1>

<img style="float:right;" src="https://s3.asiainspection.com/images/news/CHB_Lab.jpg" alt="Lab Testing Services for Consumer Goods | AsiaInspection"/>

<p><b>Hong Kong, June 25, 2013</b> - AsiaInspection today announced it has completed the acquisition of CHB, a private Chinese owned <a href="/quality-control-services/laboratory-testing">lab testing</a> company. CHB is CNAS and CMA accredited and is a leader in <a href="/reach-testing">REACH</a> and <a href="/rohs-testing">RoHS testing</a>.</p>

<p>The acquisition of the CHB laboratories allows for AsiaInspection to perform in-house <a href="/quality-control-services/laboratory-testing">consumer goods testing and certification</a> in addition to its extensive experience in <a href="/">quality control</a>. AsiaInpection now offers 2,000+ testing services including <a href="/reach-testing">REACH</a>, <a href="/rohs-testing">RoHS</a> and EN 71 with industry leading 48 hour lab test report turnaround times and technical support to ensure products are compliant with international standards.</p>

<p>"AsiaInspection acquiring the CHB laboratory and their expertise in electronic, footwear, apparel and toys chemical testing will benefit clients by enhancing our lab testing network with the specialized expertise of an internationally renowned facility and further reduce risk in their supply chain," said Sebastien Breteau, CEO, AsiaInspection "In CHB, AsiaInspection clients gain the protection of an array of additional lab test protocols across the entire range of consumer goods, further eliminating risk."</p>

<h2 style="font-size:18px;">About AsiaInspection - Your Eyes in the Supply Chain!&trade;</h2>

<p><a href="/">AsiaInspection</a> is a leading quality control services provider for importers from Asia and Africa, providing web-based account management, fast scheduling and highly competitive prices for companies seeking <a href="/quality-control-services/product-and-manufacturing-inspections">Product Inspection</a>, <a href="/manufacturing-audit">Factory Audit</a> and <a href="/quality-control-services/laboratory-testing">Laboratory Testing services</a>. AsiaInspection serves clients from over 100 countries worldwide.
